## Component Location

- **Reusable components**: `src/lib/components/`
- **Page components**: `src/routes/*/+page.svelte`
- **Layout components**: `src/routes/+layout.svelte`
- **Stores**: `src/lib/stores/`
- **Utilities**: `src/lib/utils/` or `src/lib/utilities/`

## Route Components

SvelteKit uses file-based routing:

- `src/routes/+page.svelte` → `/` (home page)
- `src/routes/about/+page.svelte` → `/about`
- `src/routes/+layout.svelte` → Root layout (wraps all pages)

